column6:
Spacious, clean apartment in Cedar Park/North Austin. One large master bedroom available with bathroom and walk-in closet. The kitchen, dining area, and living room are also all yours during your stay. :) 

You're welcome to use wifi, washer/dryer (in apartment), and pool (on grounds).

25 min from downtown Austin. Walking distance from grocery, Walgreens, Sbux, and several restaurants.

We have a dog, but he'll be out of town with us. There's some road noise, but a fan drowns it out easily.
column9: Spacious, Clean Apartment: Cedar Park / N. Austin
